This images contains Java8 and AndroidSDK to build apk in a CI environment.

At the moment there is no support for running an emulator.

Each Dockefile has a version of android SDK and build-tools :

* DockerfileXX : android-XX and build-tools-XX.Y.Z (with y.z the lastest release for XX)

You can pull each of these from the Docker Hub using android version as tag :

```
$ docker pull gazeria/docker-android:XX
```

The supported android version goes from 19 to 25.

Also this images include fastlane installed.
